To access the full-text search functionality, you have to install the Semantic Search for the Microsoft SQL Server. For more information on searching in Acumatica ERP, see [HelpRoot_Administration\SM__mng_Search|Managing Search] in the Acumatica ERP System Administration Guide.{br}
