#In the file, find the <tt>providers</tt> section in <tt>membership</tt>, which has the following settings (they depend on your website settings).{{{{&lt;membership defaultProvider="PXActiveDirectorySyncMembershipProvider"&gt;
   &lt;providers&gt;
     &lt;remove name="PXActiveDirectorySyncMembershipProvider"/&gt;
     &lt;remove name="MySQLMembershipProvider" /&gt;
